OL,3,CGalloway Glens project completed after
OL,4,Cfive years of work
OL,6,FThe #6 million Galloway Glens Scheme,
OL,7,Fwhich aimed to transform life in the
OL,8,Frural heart of Dumfries and Galloway,
OL,9,Fhas now wound up after five years.
OL,11,FThe lottery money has funded projects
OL,12,Fbig and small - from creating
OL,13,Ffootpaths to archaeological surveys,
OL,14,Ftransforming farmland and forrest.
OL,16,FThose behind the project wanted it to
OL,17,Fconnect people living and working in
OL,18,Fthe area with its heritage and
OL,19,Flandscape.
