OL,6,FMcNabb Laurie, who was tasked with
OL,7,Fdelivering the Galloway Glens vision,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I went to school near Moniaive
OL,9,Fand then onto university.
OL,11,F"I was working for 10 years or so
OL,12,Facross the UK looking at geography and
OL,13,Ftrue environmental science. I ended up
OL,14,Flooking at people and how people
OL,15,Finteract with their environment.
OL,17,F"I remember coming to Loch Ken as a
OL,18,Fchild and walking up in the hills.
