OL,6,F"I like to be outdoors in the fresh
OL,7,Fair, I haven't got an urge for fancy
OL,8,Fcars it is the life you can have in
OL,9,Fthat appeals to me the most."
OL,11,FMcNabb explained the work that went on
OL,12,Fduring the project, saying: "The
OL,13,FGalloway Glens scheme is five years of
OL,14,Fco-ordinated activity. Rather than
OL,15,Fdoing a single big project you do a
OL,16,Fseries of projects in a defined area
OL,17,Fand these projects feed off of each
OL,18,Fother.
