OL,3,CGalloway Glens project completed after
OL,4,Cfive years of work
OL,6,F"By approaching them in a more co-
OL,7,Fordinated manner you end up with more
OL,8,Fthan some of the other parts. It is
OL,9,Fabout how to engage people in
OL,10,Fsometimes some of these bewildering
OL,11,Fglobal issues, we are trying to carve
OL,12,Fout a little corner.
OL,14,F"The Galloway Glens name was chosen
OL,15,Fbecause it doesn't exist. The Galloway
OL,16,FGlens varies from the wild land of the
OL,17,FGalloway Hills right around to Loch
OL,18,FKen and and then right out to sea.
