OL,3,CGalloway Glens project completed after
OL,4,Cfive years of work
OL,6,F"We are connected by the hydro scheme
OL,7,Freally. It has given the landscape a
OL,8,Fspecial quality in terms of the loch's
OL,9,Fand the lakes. We pull together this
OL,10,Fpackage to showcase that the valley is
OL,11,Fspecial and that allowed us to get the
OL,12,Flottery funding to do all of the work."
OL,14,FAfter five years working on the
OL,15,Fproject McNabb cherishes his time
OL,16,Fspent in the region.
