OL,3,CGalloway Glens project completed after
OL,4,Cfive years of work
OL,6,FHe said: "I wouldn't want to work
OL,7,Fanywhere else and I feel so lucky that
OL,8,FI have spent the last five years
OL,9,Flearning more about this valley and I
OL,10,Fget paid for it as well.
OL,12,F"The whole thing, I am so so lucky. My
OL,13,Fchildren think my job is going around
OL,14,Fand cutting ribbons but there is a lot
OL,15,Fof work that goes on behind the
OL,16,Fscenes."
